0.1.name: wordpress/deregister-contact-form-7
0.1.description: Prevents the scripts and styling from the Contact Form 7 plugin from loading on your site. Useful for situations in which you do not require the AJAX functionality of the original plugin and have included all the necessary styling in your themes CSS.
